              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two different types of spectrometers were used-",
                "The right-side one -Two plastic scintilators,3 mm thick",
                "and 5 mm thick and a BGO scintillator, 60 mm in",
                "diameter and 200 mm long for 20 degree and 160 mm long",
                "for 40, 70 and 105 degree connected with",
                "photomultiplier tubes(PMTs).",
                "The left-side one-(low-energy module) consisted of two",
                "silicon layer, 50 mum thick and either 2000 mum thick",
                "for 105 degree or 300 mum thick for 20, 40 and 70",
                "degrees and two scintillation counters, a cubic CsI(Tl)",
                " 40 mm long scintillator and a plate plastic",
                "scintillator, 5 mm thick, connected with PMTs."
              ]
